	<h1 class="title">投票＋直播，《中国正在听》能再创超女辉煌吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/999/small/999.jpg?1404052188" alt="">
